      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently maintained to ensure reliable performance. The exterior looks great overall, though it does show some minor signs of use, including a few small stone chips on the hood and light surface scratches typical for its age. Inside, the upholstery is clean with some minor wear on the driver\u2019s seat, but all features and electronics are in perfect working order. It drives smoothly and would make an excellent, dependable car for anyone looking for a well-cared-for vehicle.",
      "price": 34500.0,
