      "description": "We are proud to present this exceptional vehicle, currently maintained in pristine, showroom condition. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the meticulously preserved interior, reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the market. This is more than just a pre-owned car; it is a testament to automotive excellence, offering the performance and aesthetic of a brand-new model. For the buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle represents an unparalleled investment in quality and reliability.",
      "price": 48900.0,
